block vars

block main
  h1.p-hr__label--logo
    +logo

  p.p-hr__box--description
    | We are Hamon Radio - an independent internet radio station based in Tokyo.
    | We started Hamon Radio to create a third place where people of all the world share and communicate with each other via music we select from the world, particularly Japan.
    | "Hamon" means ripple in Japanese.When a drip falls in water, the ripple expands gently and gradually turns to greater influence.
    | We hope Hamon Radio can be like this very first drip.

  div.p-hr__box--contents
